graph LR
    classDef ui fill:#f9f5ff,stroke:#6941c6,stroke-width:2px,color:#101828;
    classDef agent fill:#f0f9ff,stroke:#026aa7,stroke-width:2px,color:#101828;
    classDef cache fill:#fffaeb,stroke:#b54708,stroke-width:2px,color:#101828;
    classDef db fill:#ecfdf3,stroke:#027a48,stroke-width:2px,color:#101828;

    UI[Streamlit Client]:::ui
    Router[Retrieval Router]:::agent
    Ollama[Local LLM Embedding]:::agent
    Chroma[(ChromaDB)]:::db
    State[Local JSON State]:::cache

    UI -->|Create Session| State
    UI -->|Send Query| Router
    Router -->|If Follow-up| Ollama
    Ollama -->|Vectorize Query| Chroma
    Chroma -->|Return Top N Past Evidence| Router
    Router -->|Merge with New Search Data| UI
    Router -->|Save New Evidence| Chroma
    UI -->|Export Session| State
